      "index": 1,
      "text": "Yes, Lady Arano. I grew up on Nassau Heights—one of the orbital hab stations above the planet's surface.\n\nNobody makes landfall except for the surface mining teams, and they stay only for month-long shifts. It's too dangerous for permanent habitation.",
