        "id": "9c030b0cc0c0ef31f4cd8c2b"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Yes, Lady Arano. It's a gremlin story, something the miners can blame when they pass out drunk with the headlights running. \"The Locura killed my engine, I barely got out alive!\"\n\nNot our proudest achievement as a culture, but apparently it gets around.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 4,
          "hideIfUnavailable": false,
