      "text": "Don't worry—you won't. Not where you'll be dropping.\n\nSurface teams tend to cluster around the rocky outcrops that ring the planet's equator. That's where you find all the really good stuff—the platinum, the ruthenium, the rarer exotics. You'll be well clear of the mining zones.",
