        "id": "9c00aebe1d70a8d60ae345b5"
      },
      "index": 11,
      "text": "If we act quickly enough, it won't matter who they are. We'll get in, loot the armory, and be on our way before they even make planetfall.\n\nWe don't have time to play this safe, so we're dropping now. I want our 'Mechs on the ground when the doors open. I'll inform Captain Grigas of the change.",
