        "id": "9c1ccdd0b37b539ffe07cb97"
      },
      "index": 13,
      "text": "You can't go down there in person, Kamea… and certainly not before we're sure it's safe.\n\nYou're the leader of the Restoration. We can't afford to lose you on a salvage operation.",
      "branches": [
